1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
We are already using our phones to code.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:12,000
The laptop is not required anymore.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:19,500
Your code and repository can live directly in the cloud.

4
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:27,000
You can make changes there and commit them back to your repo.

5
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:36,000
With coding agents, the physical machine matters less.

6
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:46,000
In the future, I may not need my laptop to code.
